WEBVTT

00:05.008 --> 00:07.576
Are you guys reading books?

00:09.212 --> 00:11.179
Since Austin's world
tour starts in a week,

00:11.181 --> 00:13.281
I'm helping him learn
some foreign languages.

00:13.283 --> 00:15.517
I can ask, "where
are the pancakes?"

00:15.519 --> 00:17.152
In fifteen different languages.

00:17.154 --> 00:18.487
French...

00:21.691 --> 00:22.991
Mandarin...

00:24.661 --> 00:26.194
Even pig Latin.

00:26.196 --> 00:29.364
"Ere-whay are-ay
e-thay ancakes-pay?"

00:31.701 --> 00:33.535
You guys are a
couple of oof-days.

00:35.038 --> 00:37.039
What's with the animal
print pillows?Ãš

00:37.041 --> 00:38.874
I'm turning the practice
room into my new office.

00:38.876 --> 00:40.942
What gives you the right?

00:42.412 --> 00:44.212
Dez, calm down.

00:44.214 --> 00:47.916
She'll be running the music factory while
I'm at school and Austin's on tour.

00:47.918 --> 00:49.317
What do you care anyway?

00:49.319 --> 00:51.887
You'll be finishing film school
and hanging out with Carrie

00:51.889 --> 00:54.322
way on the other
side of the country.

00:54.324 --> 00:56.058
Oh, I can't wait.

00:56.060 --> 00:58.093
Aw, I'm going to miss you too.

00:58.095 --> 00:59.761
I'm going to miss all you guys.

00:59.763 --> 01:02.731
Well, no matter where
life takes us,

01:02.733 --> 01:05.099
we'll always have this place
to bring us together.

01:05.102 --> 01:07.569
And luckily, we'll have Trish
to take really good care of it.

01:07.571 --> 01:10.439
And I promise to make the
school my top priority.

01:10.441 --> 01:13.742
Trish, it's so great that you're
taking this so seriously.

01:13.744 --> 01:18.146
Nothing means more to me than than
the A&A music... oh, my hot tub!

01:20.183 --> 01:22.084
What? It's for my new office.

01:22.086 --> 01:24.419
It'll fit. I just got to
get rid of the piano...

01:24.421 --> 01:26.254
And all that music junk.

